  "description": "Product Description The Pride &amp; Groom deodorising doggie spray has been specifically designed to easily freshen up your pets skin and coat. The doggie spray allows for you to keep your pet smelling fresh and clean between baths and can be used on all breeds. The doggie spray has a fresh fragrance that includes aloe vera and tea tree oil. The spray requires no water or rinsing and it's a must-have for any dog owner so that your dog is smelling fresh and adds nourishment to their skin and coat. In an easy to use 200ml pump spray, small enough for a handbag. Directions 1. Shake the bottle well before use. 2. Hold the bottle 15-20 cm away from your dog. 3. Spray a light mist over your dog's coat, avoiding the eyes and mouth. 4. Brush your dog gently to ensure even distribution. 5. Repeat as needed for persistent odors. Safety Warning For External Use Only See more",
